title: National gathering of Puerto Ricans seeks to pressure Congress, Obama
text: Puerto Rican political, faith and civic leaders will convene in Orlando for a national meeting this week to develop a political agenda to pressure the federal government into taking action to help solve the island's fiscal crisis.
